<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #374151;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .email-address {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #111827;">Confirm Your New Email Address</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p>You requested to change your email address to <span class="email-address"><%= @new_email %></span>.</p>
    
    <p>To confirm this change, please click the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <%= link_to "Confirm email change", @confirmation_url, class: "button" %>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
      Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <%= @confirmation_url %>
    </p>
    
    <p style="color: #dc2626; font-size: 14px;">
      <strong>This link will expire in 30 minutes.</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p>If you didn't request this change, you can safely ignore this email. Your current email address will remain unchanged.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent to <%= @new_email %> because you requested to change your email address.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
